data.meta_description: NandaNgr-031111 - Free ebook download as Excel Spreadsheet (.xls), PDF File (.pdf), Text File (.txt) or read book online for free. The document lists 91 rejected applicants for various medical positions along with the reasons for rejection. The positions include staff nurse, nursing orderly, pharmacist, radiographer, lab assistant, and others. For most applicants, the reason given is "application form not found" or "documents not received". A few other reasons provided include "wrong entry" and "only application form found".
